      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p>For procedural primitives, RenderMan for Blender supports both procedural primitive DSOs and RunProgram. For more information on how to write/compile these types of procedural primitives see this <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN/pages/19859932\" rel=\"nofollow\">section</a> in the Developer's Guide.</p><h2 id=\"ProceduralPrimitivesinBlender-Adding\">Adding</h2><p>You can add either type of procedural primitive from the Add menu.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"775\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637646/procprim_add.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432693844&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=236\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637646/procprim_add.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432693844&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"236\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637660\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"procprim_add.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637646\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"602308d5-3f2e-4ba2-b03d-5733378bed8e\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637646/procprim_add.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432693844&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=236 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637646/procprim_add.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432693844&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=236 1x\"></span><p /><h3 id=\"ProceduralPrimitivesinBlender-DSO\">DSO</h3><p>To pass arguments to your RunProgram look in the object properties <span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" height=\"28\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637646/object_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432694049&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=24&amp;height=28\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637646/object_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432694049&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637669\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"object_properties.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637646\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"8bd1e6dc-ca20-46e0-b1bd-033453abd440\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637646/object_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432694049&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=24&amp;height=28 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637646/object_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432694049&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=24&amp;height=28 1x\"></span>, under the RenderMan Geometry panel; there should be a Dynamic Load DSO subpanel.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"775\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637646/dso_args.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432693844&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=407&amp;height=92\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637646/dso_args.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432693844&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"92\" data-width=\"407\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637666\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"dso_args.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637646\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"6d56a7f9-812a-456c-8782-26b731062216\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637646/dso_args.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432693844&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=407&amp;height=92 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637646/dso_args.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432693844&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=407&amp;height=92 1x\"></span>"
    }
